title.rendered: Couture designer ZIAD NAKAD dress Amandine Petit, Miss France 2021 for the Final of MISS UNIVERSE

content.rendered:
Amandine Petit, Miss France 2021 was dressed by couture designer Ziad Nakad for the final of Miss Universe Sunday, May 16th in Hollywood Florida USA.

Photography Anthony Passant Talent Lab Paris
